column1:
Speaker Pelosi: Focused on taking down @realDonaldTrump at any cost.

@POTUS: Focused on securing better trade deals for hardworking Americans.

The contrast couldn't be any more clear.

Robert Kennedy Jr. is a scion of America’s storied political family. He’s also a conspiracy theorist and a manifestation of post-pandemic politics. 

@rtraister reports on the Kennedys’ “perpetual problem child” — and his disruptive presidential campaign:
https://trib.al/3gKrl5M

America needs a unifying and experienced leader, who can and wants to make life better for everyone everywhere. 

@JoeBiden is that leader.

I know that from experience, more than can fit in a tweet:

COVID-19 was unleashed onto the world by China. 
 
@SpeakerPelosi now sides with Communist China by calling it the "Trump Virus."

Nancy, we’re both old enough to know what I mean when I say you’ve officially “jumped the shark.”

